description:
This is a market on whether Bored Ape Yacht Club (BAYC) will have a floor price of 70 ETH or above on August 31, 2022 (at 12:00 PM ET), according to https://opensea.io/collection/boredapeyachtclub.  

This market will resolve to "Yes" if, on the aforementioned check time, there are no Bored Apes listed for sale ("Buy now") for less than 70 ETH on the official Bored Ape Yacht Club (BAYC) collection page on OpenSea. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".  

Only listings that have existed for at least an hour are valid for this market. List time for an NFT can be found under “Trading History” by clicking the “Listing” filter and hovering over the date.  

Note that the exact price at the check time will be used. If the collection is not available to check on OpenSea at the check time, the market will be checked an hour later, using listings which existed for at least an hour to that check time. If still unavailable, the market will resolve 50-50. For valid listings that are declining price auctions, the price exactly at the check time will be used, NOT the price at the initial listing time.
